                  House, Club, Progressive | Silk Royal Records

            320 kbps | MP3 | Mixed + Split | 2014 | 02:38:20 | 729 Mb



Silk Royal is truly privileged to receive radio support from the industry elite, including: Kyau & Albert, Super8 & Tab, Max Graham, Solarstone, Boom Jinx, Jaytech, and Ruben de Ronde. We look forward to releasing intelligent and emotional dancefloor-oriented music for years to come."The compilation is inspired by our weekly radio show of the same name, which is co-hosted by Jacob and Tom, as well as veteran label talents Ad Brown and Zack Roth. Reaching international listeners on Proton Radio, Dance Paradise, and other radio platforms, Silk Royal Showcase is quickly approaching its 250th episode and now often ranks amongst the Top 100 Podcasts in the world on iTunes.
